<lb ed="X" n="0544b04"/>利<note place="inline">三十八</note><note place="inline">此是觀世音菩薩。把牌弩弓箭也</note>　罰沙罰&CB00072;<note place="inline">三十九</note><note place="inline">同前</note>　佛囉舍耶
<lb ed="X" n="0544b05"/><note place="inline">四十</note><note place="inline">此是阿彌陀佛本身。觀世音菩薩師主</note>　呼盧呼盧摩囉<note place="inline">四十一</note><note place="inline">此是八部鬼神王</note>
<lb ed="X" n="0544b06"/>　呼盧呼盧醯唎<note place="inline">四十二</note><note place="inline">同前</note>　娑囉娑囉<note place="inline">四十三</note><note place="inline">此是五濁惡世也</note>　悉唎
<lb ed="X" n="0544b07"/>悉唎<note place="inline">四十四</note><note place="inline">此是觀世音菩薩利益一切眾生不可思議</note>　蘇嚧蘇嚧<note place="inline">四十五</note><note place="inline">此是諸佛樹
<lb ed="X" n="0544b08"/>葉落聲</note>　菩提夜菩提夜<note place="inline">四十六</note><note place="inline">此是觀世音菩薩結緣眾生</note>　菩&CB00501;夜菩&CB00501;
