<lb ed="X" n="0544b11"/>是也</note>　波夜摩那<note place="inline">五十一</note><note place="inline">此是寶金光幢菩薩鈸折羅杵</note>　娑婆訶<note place="inline">去聲</note><note place="inline">五十二</note>　悉
<lb ed="X" n="0544b12"/>陀夜<note place="inline">五十三</note><note place="inline">此是達一切法門</note>　娑婆訶<note place="inline">去聲</note><note place="inline">五十四</note>　摩訶悉陀夜<note place="inline">五十五</note>
