<lb ed="X" n="0544b15"/>囉謹墀<note place="inline">六十</note><note place="inline">山海慧菩薩本身。手把金刀</note>　娑婆訶<note place="inline">去聲</note><note place="inline">六十一</note>　摩羅那羅
<lb ed="X" n="0544b16"/><note place="inline">六十二</note><note place="inline">此是寶<note n="0544002" resp="Xuzangjing" place="foot text" type="orig">即王疑印手</note>〔即〕王菩薩手把金斧</note>　娑婆訶<note place="inline">去聲</note><note place="inline">六十三</note>　悉囉僧阿穆佉耶
